fields.service_Description: PUP QC has Registrar's office that handles students' registrations
PUP QC has libraries to give students access on some books to assist them on their research paper
PUP QC has a medic on standby and receives patient or health related concerns.
PUP QC has it's student support with Adviser, and Counselors available for helping students with their concerns.
PUP QC has Student Services to provide for students in need of Financial Aid, Scholarship, ID Request/Concerns, and ongoing Elections and Government
PUP QC has services such as Medical Support/Insurance, Lost and Found services, Parking routes, permits and guidelines, and Housing accommodation/Living Assistance.
